00:14:58.399 --> 00:14:59.299 position:35% line:89% align:start
[ALL gasp]

00:14:59.433 --> 00:15:00.568 position:41% line:83% align:start
[ALICE]
Too close to floor seven!

00:15:01.068 --> 00:15:02.035 position:19% line:83% align:start
[MALE PARTY CAPTAIN 2A]
It wasn't supposed

00:15:02.169 --> 00:15:03.337 position:27% line:89% align:start
to be like this.

00:15:03.470 --> 00:15:05.406 position:35% line:83% align:start
-Uh? Wait!
-[EVE] Carrot?

00:15:05.973 --> 00:15:07.274 position:30% line:89% align:start
You mean that?

00:15:07.408 --> 00:15:08.877 position:10% line:83% align:start
You're really going to let me
join your group?

00:15:09.009 --> 00:15:11.278 position:44% line:83% align:start
Yes,
you have a lot of potential,

00:15:11.412 --> 00:15:13.815 position:10% line:83% align:start
and potential can only shine
in a dungeon!

00:15:13.947 --> 00:15:15.182 position:33% line:89% align:start
He's hideous.

00:15:15.315 --> 00:15:17.951 position:13% line:89% align:start
Oh, well, yeah. Poor girl.

00:15:18.085 --> 00:15:19.219 position:16% line:89% align:start
She's been asking around

00:15:19.353 --> 00:15:21.121 position:16% line:83% align:start
for adventurer companions
lately,

00:15:21.255 --> 00:15:23.223 position:5% line:89% align:start
but her max level is only a two.

00:15:23.357 --> 00:15:25.459 position:13% line:83% align:start
That's why everyone's been
turning her down.

00:15:25.593 --> 00:15:26.561 position:38% line:89% align:start
Come on.

00:15:26.694 --> 00:15:28.061 position:19% line:83% align:start
Let's chase our dreams
in the dungeons.

00:15:28.195 --> 00:15:29.196 position:41% line:83% align:start
[RYOTA]
Not a good idea.

00:15:29.329 --> 00:15:30.931 position:21% line:89% align:start
And what do you want?

00:15:31.064 --> 00:15:33.133 position:16% line:83% align:start
I want to take this girl
for my party.

00:15:33.267 --> 00:15:35.269 position:19% line:89% align:start
Who, me? Are you sure?

00:15:35.402 --> 00:15:38.138 position:10% line:83% align:start
-I'm not leaving without her.
-Hm...

00:15:38.272 --> 00:15:40.007 position:41% line:83% align:start
[RYOTA]
Especially while you're here.

00:15:40.140 --> 00:15:41.175 position:35% line:89% align:start
[whimpers]

00:15:41.910 --> 00:15:46.013 position:5% line:83% align:start
Wow! You must be really talented
to be joining Ryota's party!

00:15:46.146 --> 00:15:47.582 position:30% line:89% align:start
Congrats, kid!

00:15:47.715 --> 00:15:49.416 position:13% line:83% align:start
What an honor to be invited
into the Ryota Family!

00:15:49.551 --> 00:15:51.452 position:16% line:83% align:start
They're the hottest party
in town right now!

00:15:51.586 --> 00:15:54.388 position:7% line:83% align:start
You are a seriously lucky girl!
Go get them!

00:15:54.522 --> 00:15:56.957 position:10% line:89% align:start
You think I'm lucky? Really?

00:15:57.090 --> 00:15:59.627 position:5% line:89% align:start
Yes! You're in the Ryota Family!

00:15:59.761 --> 00:16:02.697 position:10% line:83% align:start
Guess it's that "Ryota Sato"
people talk about.

00:16:02.831 --> 00:16:04.097 position:24% line:89% align:start
The guy from Selen?

00:16:04.231 --> 00:16:05.999 position:41% line:83% align:start
[ALICE]
Is he a big deal or something?

00:16:06.400 --> 00:16:08.503 position:5% line:89% align:start
Oh, yeah! That guy's everywhere!

00:16:08.903 --> 00:16:10.003 position:47% line:89% align:start
Ah!

00:16:10.939 --> 00:16:12.039 position:38% line:89% align:start
[scoffs]

00:16:13.440 --> 00:16:14.274 position:41% line:89% align:start
[sighs]

00:16:14.408 --> 00:16:16.210 position:16% line:83% align:start
-Thanks, Erza. I owe you.
-Uh.

00:16:16.343 --> 00:16:17.512 position:38% line:83% align:start
-You do?
-Yep.

00:16:17.645 --> 00:16:18.646 position:35% line:89% align:start
Okay, kid.

00:16:19.079 --> 00:16:20.715 position:19% line:83% align:start
Want to officially join
my party?

00:16:20.849 --> 00:16:21.982 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yes.

00:16:22.115 --> 00:16:23.651 position:19% line:89% align:start
Well, what's your name?

00:16:23.785 --> 00:16:24.953 position:35% line:89% align:start
I'm Alice.

00:16:25.085 --> 00:16:27.087 position:35% line:83% align:start
Hey, Alice.
My name's Ryota Sato.

00:16:27.454 --> 00:16:29.924 position:7% line:83% align:start
-Pleasure to have you on board.
-Thanks!

00:16:30.057 --> 00:16:32.727 position:35% line:89% align:start
[footsteps]

00:16:33.160 --> 00:16:34.796 position:21% line:89% align:start
All right, first up.

00:16:34.929 --> 00:16:36.931 position:50% line:89% align:start
âª

00:16:37.064 --> 00:16:38.800 position:13% line:89% align:start
Can you try touching this?

00:16:38.933 --> 00:16:40.133 position:35% line:89% align:start
Sure thing.

